Content:
I have these carbs that were really back and covered in filth. I gave em a good long soak in the ultrasonic cleaner and noticed this nasty white film clung to the side of the carb bodies.

I blasted them and they came out great... I thought maybe I should put em back in the cleaner real quick just to get any bits off butnwjen they dried the film was back... ( like a dummy used the same wash liquid) but what is this stuff?
